title: Jedi Mind Tricks Discography
description:
Sorry about the last one, I noticed an error I&#039;ll detail later.

Most JMT discographies I&#039;ve seen are either missing albums, songs, or include some albums not made by JMT.  So I pieced this together.  It includes:

The Psycho-Social
Violent by Design
Visions of Gandhi
Legacy of Blood
Servants in Heaven, Kings in Hell

In Servants, tracks 4, 13, and 14 (Uncommon Valor, Outlive the War, and Gutta Music) have 2 copies.  When I first downloaded the album these were flawed files, and couldn&#039;t play.  My brief attempts at removing them failed, so I just included them anyway.  The second copy of each is fine, however.  This is also why I had to re-upload this, the first time I forgot to move over the good files.  Apologies for any inconveniences.
